**Idea:** 
* This is a variation of a classic CS problem called [Fractional Knapsack](https://www.tutorialspoint.com/design_and_analysis_of_algorithms/design_and_analysis_of_algorithms_fractional_knapsack.htm). I'd highly recommend reading about it.
* Maximize the units you can take by sorting boxTypes in descending order
* Keep taking boxes as long as there is space in truck i.e. truck size > 0
>**T/S:** O(n lg n)/O(1), where n = size(boxTypes)
