Basically we need to load the heaviest box first to get the optimal solution. So we need to sort the box based on the weight.
```
    public int maximumUnits(int[][] boxTypes, int truckSize) {
        Arrays.sort(boxTypes, (a, b) -> b[1] - a[1]); // Sort the box reversely.
        int ans = 0, index = 0;
        while (truckSize > 0) {
            if (truckSize > boxTypes[index][0]) {
                truckSize -= boxTypes[index][0];
                ans += boxTypes[index][1] * boxTypes[index][0];
                index++;
                if (index == boxTypes.length) break; // If load all boxes, break immediately to avoid out of boundary.
            } else {
                ans += boxTypes[index][1] * truckSize;
                truckSize = 0;
            }
        }
        return ans;        
    }
